SELECT 
    cliente_id,
    nome,
    email,
    telefone,
    total_compras,
    numero_compras,
    CASE 
        WHEN total_compras >= 10000 AND numero_compras >= 50 THEN 'VIP'
        ELSE 'Regular'
    END AS categoria
FROM clientes
WHERE total_compras >= 10000 OR numero_compras >= 50
ORDER BY total_compras DESC, numero_compras DESC;

create or replace function CMDKLTD_CMDK_AUTO_FUNCTION_TEST_GUARD (nr_seq_reserva_p	Number)
    nm_secret_p      IN   VARCHAR2,
    nm_usuario_p     IN   VARCHAR2,
    nm_partnerid_p   IN   VARCHAR2
) IS
    v_count NUMBER;
BEGIN
    SELECT
        COUNT(*)
    INTO v_count
    FROM
        EXAM_LAB_ORDER;
    IF v_count > 0 THEN
        UPDATE EXAM_LAB_ORDER
        SET
            dt_atualizacao = sysdate,
            nm_usuario = nm_usuario_p,
            nm_secret = nm_secret_p
end CMDKLTD_CMDK_AUTO_FUNCTION_TEST_GUARD;
